ngram\": \"weights\", \"from\": 5035, \"to\": 5042}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5052, \"to\": 5061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is something where everyone is on an equal footing.\\\"\", \"from\": 5068, \"to\": 5125, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5076, \"to\": 5085}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 5092, \"to\": 5100}, {\"ngram\": \"an equal footing\", \"from\": 5107, \"to\": 5123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For years he got better and better and then in 2008 he got invited to the Olympics for the first time.\", \"from\": 5127, \"to\": 5229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 5131, \"to\": 5136}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5197, \"to\": 5209}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 5214, \"to\": 5228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Photo by Brittany Nelson/USA Shooting \\\"My most memorable experience was when I walked in to compete on my first day of competition, when I walked onto the field of play.\", \"from\": 5231, \"to\": 5401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5240, \"end\": 5255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittany_Nelson\", \"score\": 0.9999983666425275, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brittany Nelson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittany_Nelson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittany_Nelson\"}, {\"begin\": 5256, \"end\": 5268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Shooting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USA Shooting\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Shooting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Shooting\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Photo\", \"from\": 5231, \"to\": 5236}, {\"ngram\": \"My most memorable experience\", \"from\": 5270, \"to\": 5298}, {\"ngram\": \"my first day\", \"from\": 5334, \"to\": 5346}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 5350, \"to\": 5361}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 5382, \"to\": 5391}, {\"ngram\": \"play\", \"from\": 5395, \"to\": 5399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I did it for the Olympics representing America, it was a different world.\\\"\", \"from\": 5402, \"to\": 5481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5420, \"to\": 5432}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 5446, \"to\": 5453}, {\"ngram\": \"a different world\", \"from\": 5462, \"to\": 5479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sanderson hit his peak in the years after those Olympics, eventually becoming number one in the world in the late ought's, but injuries, miscues, and a string of bad luck kept him from performing to his standards in the 2012 and 2016 games.\", \"from\": 5483, \"to\": 5723, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sanderson\", \"from\": 5483, \"to\": 5492}, {\"ngram\": \"his peak\", \"from\": 5497, \"to\": 5505}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 5509, \"to\": 5518}, {\"ngram\": \"those Olympics\", \"from\": 5525, \"to\": 5539}, {\"ngram\": \"number\", \"from\": 5561, \"to\": 5567}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5575, \"to\": 5584}, {\"ngram\": \"the late ought\", \"from\": 5588, \"to\": 5602}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 5610, \"to\": 5618}, {\"ngram\": \"miscues\", \"from\": 5620, \"to\": 5627}, {\"ngram\": \"a string\", \"from\": 5633, \"to\": 5641}, {\"ngram\": \"bad luck\", \"from\": 5645, \"to\": 5653}, {\"ngram\": \"his standards\", \"from\": 5682, \"to\": 5695}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2012 and 2016 games\", \"from\": 5699, \"to\": 5722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He says he has been improving day by day and thinks he is primed for a good showing in Paris.\", \"from\": 5725, \"to\": 5818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5812, \"end\": 5817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999928186298, \"rank\": 7.181374998633354e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 5762, \"to\": 5765}, {\"ngram\": \"a good showing\", \"from\": 5794, \"to\": 5808}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also says he has some simple advice for young aspiring Olympians.\", \"from\": 5820, \"to\": 5888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some simple advice\", \"from\": 5840, \"to\": 5858}, {\"ngram\": \"young aspiring Olympians\", \"from\": 5863, \"to\": 5887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Each day just suck less,\\\" he said semi-jokingly.\", \"from\": 5890, \"to\": 5939, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You do not have to be perfect, you just have to get better.\\\"\", \"from\": 5940, \"to\": 6001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you want to catch Sanderson and the rest of Team USA at the Olympics, he is competing in the 25 meter rapid fire pistol events.\", \"from\": 6003, \"to\": 6133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6024, \"end\": 6033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_William_Sanderson\", \"score\": 0.7819102661943991, \"rank\": 0.2756567536920536, \"text\": \"Sanderson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_William_Sanderson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_William_Sanderson\"}, {\"begin\": 6050, \"end\": 6058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9620793092401227, \"rank\": 0.03899730667831039, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 6038, \"to\": 6046}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 6062, \"to\": 6074}, {\"ngram\": \"the 25 meter rapid fire pistol events\", \"from\": 6095, \"to\": 6132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pre-event training is on Saturday.\", \"from\": 6135, \"to\": 6169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pre-event training\", \"from\": 6135, \"to\": 6153}, {\"